metadata.name: Golden Xyrynx
metadata.description:
Here are images of birds that we observe through the foliage. For two years, the forest has been the heart of creativity. What if we create a being, an heir of the place, a creature of the synthesis of observation?

The act of calling Xlyrix out of oblivion will become a lament for past and inevitable future losses. 

The project is dedicated to the study of aesthetic approaches of GAN and the use of such approaches in the creation of synthetic image.
